w" src="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3a494104-ffb5-4b74-b83e-04637d378168/essay-final-pax126229.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto"/></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-1 bLA-dMf"><div class="sc-d56bc236-8 gArifC"><div class="sc-d56bc236-5 bOIDUu"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span class="sc-d56bc236-4 gKlMxC">Save</span></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-3 iOJnhy eIqCxs">essay</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-2 iOJnhy llXHdp">Music</p></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-10 tdBWn">Folk music was never green</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-11 hYbLtW">Don’t be swayed by the sound of environmental protest: these songs were first sung in the voice of the cutter, not the tree</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-12 iOJnhy dFhhBp">Richard Smyth</p></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-6 kQroYe"><span class="sc-d56bc236-7 ksqojN"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-comment-bubble" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.303,16.553l1.107,3.783l-3.48-2.322c-0.689,0.234-1.422,0.371-2.193,0.371c-1.041,0-2.024-0.234-2.907-0.642 c2.034-1.697,3.333-4.275,3.333-7.166c0-1.994-0.625-3.836-1.677-5.347c0.406-0.073,0.823-0.117,1.251-0.117 c3.762,0,6.814,2.971,6.814,6.634c0,1.594-0.578,3.057-1.539,4.2L21.303,16.553z M15.255,10.684c0,3.861-3.213,6.99-7.176,6.99 c-0.812,0-1.583-0.144-2.31-0.391l-3.667,2.446l1.166-3.985l-0.744-0.638c-1.013-1.203-1.621-2.743-1.621-4.423 c0-3.858,3.215-6.987,7.176-6.987C12.042,3.696,15.255,6.825,15.255,10.684z"></path></svg></span></div></div></a><a href="/essays/could-we-recover-the-radical-vision-of-a-free-and-united-europe"><div class="sc-d56bc236-9 eCvrmh"><div type="essay" class="sc-82db9615-2 kSWDpk"><img alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=1200&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1200w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=1920&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1920w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=2048&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 2048w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 3840w" src="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/3bb34c98-e21d-4a73-9a37-e6305764f05c/this-essay-4850005.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto"/></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-1 bLA-dMf"><div class="sc-d56bc236-8 gArifC"><div class="sc-d56bc236-5 ZcrSZ"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span class="sc-d56bc236-4 gKlMxC">Save</span></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-3 iOJnhy eIqCxs">essay</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-2 iOJnhy llXHdp">Nations and empires</p></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-10 tdBWn">A United States of Europe</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-11 hYbLtW">A free and unified Europe was first imagined by Italian radicals in the 19th century. Could we yet see their dream made real?</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-12 iOJnhy dFhhBp">Fernanda Gallo</p></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-6 kQroYe"></div></div></a></div></div></div></div><footer class="sc-8723d312-0 fVfKHB footer" data-test="footer"><div class="sc-ae266dcd-0 sc-8723d312-1 bwTVbW dRXxEN"><div class="sc-1b596d24-0 ithRRD"><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC dmJOTI"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/essays" class="sc-6908471c-0 jiLkxT">Essays</a><a href="/ideas" class="sc-6908471c-0 jiLkxT">Ideas</a><a href="/videos" class="sc-6908471c-0 jiLkxT">Videos</a></nav></div><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC dmJOTI"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/about" class="sc-6908471c-0 jiLkxT">About</a><a href="/contact" class="sc-6908471c-0 jiLkxT">Contact</a><a href="/support" class="sc-6908471c-0 jiLkxT">Support</a></nav></div><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC gSiEIv"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/feed.rss" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="sc-6908471c-0 jiLkxT">RSS Feed</a><a data-ga-select-promotion="aeon_footer_donate" href="/donate" class="sc-6908471c-0 jiLkxT">Donate</a><a href="/community-guidelines" class="sc-6908471c-0 jiLkxT">Community Guidelines</a></nav></div></div><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-89e3ac83-0 dpJmnC eajVBX"><